        <span class="pcard-tag">Intelligence</span>
        <h3 class="pcard-h">On-chip learning</h3>
        <p class="pcard-p">Traditional systems retrain offline in batches, then redeploy. Catalyst processors run STDP, BTDP, and programmable learning rules directly in silicon, adapting in real time, on-device.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3: EDGE-NATIVE (image left) -->
    <div class="pcard anim">

      <div class="pcard-img">
        <div class="bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/586063/pexels-photo-586063.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900')"></div>
        <div class="fade"></div>
